<?xml version="1.0"?><opml version="2.0"><head><ownerEmail>rausterberry@gmail.com</ownerEmail></head><body><outline text="as availability setter I want to log in once and stay logged in (or have single click re-login) to reduce friction"></outline><outline text="As organiser I want to adopt a taxonomy from other groups if possible so I don't have to reinvent the wheel"></outline><outline text="as availability setter I want a dialog box allowing import of supplier availability lists OR setting availability manually so complex work can be automated with a manual entry fallback if needed"><outline text="as availability setter I want supplier lists uploaded and deciphered so I can then make targeted decisions on what is made available to members"></outline><outline text="as app I need to parse multiple formats of availability lists into a highly structured beans format to enable further flexible views and queries"><outline text="as app I need manual review of decisions I can't automate when parsing availability lists so I can build the necessary data structures correctly"></outline></outline></outline><outline text="as availability setter I want to 'select and filter' available items several ways to enable swift decisions on what to cull"><outline text="as availability setter I want each 'cull' choice to be a one-click operation to save time"></outline><outline text="as availability setter I want each 'cull' view (particular combination of selection and filters) to be optionally automated to cut down on repetitive work"></outline></outline><outline text="As app I need to have long-term order and invoice data divorced from the taxonomy to allow changes or deletion of taxonomy items"></outline><outline text="As auditor I want to see monthly, quarterly and yearly summary data and all bank details, invoices and receipts to ensure no monkey business."></outline><outline text="As organiser I want to see summary information from each order cycle to gauge financial and logistical health of food group"></outline><outline text="As adjuster I want configurable templates to allow slicing of data in many ways so I can drill quickly to what I want, and have similar info at hand next time also."></outline><outline text="As member I want to access order and invoice history along with payment history and current balance so I can clarify financial situation."></outline></body></opml>